```dockerfile
# Stage 1: Build frontend
FROM node:18-alpine AS frontend-builder

WORKDIR /app/frontend

COPY frontend/package.json frontend/package-lock.json ./

RUN npm ci

COPY frontend/ .

RUN npm run build

# Stage 2: Build Python dependencies
FROM python:3.12-slim AS python-builder

WORKDIR /app

RUN pip install --no-cache-dir poetry

COPY pyproject.toml poetry.lock ./

RUN poetry config virtualenvs.in-project true && \
    poetry install --no-dev --no-root

# Stage 3: Runtime
FROM python:3.12-slim

LABEL maintainer="Analytics Platform Team" \
      description="Production Python analytics platform with React frontend"

WORKDIR /app

# Install system dependencies
RUN apt-get update && apt-get install -y --no-install-recommends \
    libpq-dev \
    unixodbc-dev \
    curl \
    && rm -rf /var/lib/apt/lists/*

# Create non-root user
RUN useradd -m -u 1000 superset

# Copy frontend static assets
COPY --from=frontend-builder /app/frontend/dist ./frontend/dist

# Copy Python virtual environment
COPY --from=python-builder /app/.venv ./.venv

# Copy application code
COPY . .

RUN chown -R superset:superset /app

USER superset

ENV PATH="/app/.venv/bin:$PATH"

EXPOSE 8088

HEALTHCHECK --interval=30s --timeout=10s --start-period=5s --retries=3 \
    CMD curl -f http://localhost:8088/health || exit 1

CMD ["gunicorn", "-w", "4", "-b", "0.0.0.0:8088", "app:create_app()"]
